# The committed .canlog fixture is a byte-exact regression baseline: a test asserts
# it stays byte-identical to its generator (FileRecorder writes LF). Pin LF and
# disable EOL conversion so it round-trips identically on every platform/checkout
# regardless of core.autocrlf.
*.canlog text eol=lf
# The committed contact-scenario golden JSON is likewise a byte-exact baseline: a test
# asserts it stays byte-identical to make_scenario_fixture (which writes LF). Pin LF so the
# committed bytes round-trip identically on every platform/checkout.
*.scenario.json text eol=lf
# The committed golden sim episode is a byte-exact baseline for the whole B2-B5 sim stack: a
# test asserts it stays byte-identical to make_sim_fixture (which writes LF). Pin LF so the
# committed bytes round-trip identically on every platform/checkout.
*.episode.txt text eol=lf
